      "name": "Gallery",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "id": "gallery_character90467",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/076815c450a0e39320b2c6b83930ae49_9135688357470686793.png",
                "imgDesc": "After you load a Blank Score, you can activate the performance device to begin a glorious on-stage performance!",
                "key": "Page 1/4"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character93733",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/feed9e71c47ca8ae6f1c0a4ed66ee829_118249082608682419.png",
                "imgDesc": "As you are performing, the stage will fire off Note Bubbles of different types.<br>If you can collect a certain number of Note Bubbles during this time, the performance will proceed normally.",
                "key": "Page 2/4"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character55376",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/e5ee33761e1df39466d24721ae586aa3_285415221991298121.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Use the power of the \"symphony\" by <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Pressing to unleash a Pause Soundwave </span>and cause the Note Bubbles to stop moving, all the better for you to collect them.<br>While you are performing, you might encounter all sorts of unexpected situations. Find a way to conquer these challenges and complete your performance.<br>Once the giant ship Fortuna in the mural reaches its destination, your performance will have reached its perfect conclusion!</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/4"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character71967",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/e2c54cbe48b632cd70bdd1b760831816_8488000790857055349.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>As the ship in the mural sails along, it will encounter storms, during which you must <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">collect Note Bubbles</span> to deploy a shield and weather the lightning. If the ship is sunk before it can deploy said shield, the performance will fail as well.<br>During a storm, the stage will also be subject to unpredictable thunderstrikes. Find a way to avoid them and complete the performance!</p>",
                "key": "Page 4/4"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
      ]
